  "body": "\r\n## Problem \r\nBy design message previews for pinned messages should contain the text of the pinned message. Currently they don't\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n![223492792-c37a35c2-f229-44e5-98c1-5ebb7d65f001](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5786310/232849900-fe311654-3cb6-4264-957d-5f54a7bf4def.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n![223498299-65e518aa-94b0-4e1a-bcbb-836990cdf0d5](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/5786310/232849935-f9832bcc-7f78-4fa2-997a-4610345d2ab0.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Open Status\r\n2) Go to 1-1 or group chat\r\n3) Send a message and pin it\r\n4) Open Status on recipient side\r\n5) Check the last message preview\r\n\r\n\r\n",
